  "detailed_description": "TOP SECRET FILE: <strong>THE STORM OF AREA 51 - 20/09/2019</strong>  <br>BURN AFTER PLAYING!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1158280/extras/ea519413d971b7d09d487440682e7b81.poster.avif?t=1575925687\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1158280/extras/ea519413d971b7d09d487440682e7b81.webm?t=1575925687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1158280/extras/ea519413d971b7d09d487440682e7b81.mp4?t=1575925687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Lead your army of fans through the defense posts of Area 51 military base. Could you be the best raid leader among your friends? Or maybe you’re the chosen one – Natural Born Legion Commander? Are you ready to accept the challenge?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1158280/extras/5e8e7aedd618f6d88fd218a5e569e271.avif?t=1575925687\" width=560 height=70 /></span><br>Run against different types of soldiers that become stronger the closer you are to Area 51 base.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1158280/extras/20dbe9ff1807971c50636c754e669483.avif?t=1575925687\" width=560 height=70 /></span><br>Place your forces effectively on the field to create invincible echelons.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1158280/extras/242b0d87e00db5333df203ad65d8c510.avif?t=1575925687\" width=560 height=70 /></span><br>Spend hype points to strengthen your Legion, combine units with different perks to create chemistry on the battlefield.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1158280/extras/f410261eb028d2e504215414bb736fef.avif?t=1575925687\" width=560 height=70 /></span><br>Catch the MLG moment to crush enemies with your special ability timing.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1158280/extras/89925073bffe187cc79cc5ec8d907ee6.avif?t=1575925687\" width=560 height=70 /></span><br>Watch them run, watch them fall - have fun!<br><br>There are just a few things you can watch forever: fire, water, and thousands of crazy fans falling while trying to raid highly guarded top-secret military facility with bare hands.",
